INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-12-11 16:47:26','2012-12-11 16:47:26','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','trash','open','open','','hello-world','','','2012-12-24 18:59:26','2012-12-24 10:59:26','',0,'http://news.pingwest.com/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2012-12-11 16:47:26','2012-12-11 16:47:26','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://news.pingwest.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2012-12-11 16:47:26','2012-12-11 16:47:26','',0,'http://news.pingwest.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(668,6,'2012-12-31 05:16:37','2012-12-30 21:16:37','多年来帮助iPhone越狱用户下载和安装破解ipa应用的Installous及其公司Hackulous今天在其官网上宣布关闭，Hackulous团队说社区陷入停滞状态，论坛基本成了空城，公司无法再继续运营。iDownloadBlog称其为“打击应用盗版的小胜利”。','iPhone越狱用户必备应用Installous及其公司Hackulous关闭','','publish','closed','closed','','iphone%e8%b6%8a%e7%8b%b1%e7%94%a8%e6%88%b7%e5%bf%85%e5%a4%87%e5%ba%94%e7%94%a8installous%e5%8f%8a%e5%85%b6%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8hackulous%e5%85%b3%e9%97%ad','','','2012-12-31 05:16:37','2012-12-30 21:16:37','',0,'http://news.pingwest.com/archives/668',0,'post','',0),(216,2,'2012-12-22 01:51:19','2012-12-22 01:51:19','Experian市场服务机构从Hitwise的2012年数据里研究了前1000个搜索项，发现“Facebook”是全美搜索量最多的检索词，这也是这家社交网络第四次成为第一名。占据了4.13%，相比2011年增长33%。','Facebook连续第四年成为全美最热门检索词','','publish','closed','open','','facebook%e8%bf%9e%e7%bb%ad%e7%ac%ac%e5%9b%9b%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%90%e4%b8%ba%e5%85%a8%e7%be%8e%e6%9c%80%e7%83%ad%e9%97%a8%e6%a3%80%e7%b4%a2%e8%af%8d','','','2012-12-24 22:15:47','2012-12-24 14:15:47','',0,'http://news.pingwest.com/facebook%e8%bf%9e%e7%bb%ad%e7%ac%ac%e5%9b%9b%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%90%e4%b8%ba%e5%85%a8%e7%be%8e%e6%9c%80%e7%83%ad%e9%97%a8%e6%a3%80%e7%b4%a2%e8%af%8d/',0,'post','',0),(5,2,'2012-12-11 01:54:32','2012-12-11 01:54:32','【暂无内容】','世界，你好！','','trash','open','open','','hello-world-2','','','2012-12-24 18:59:26','2012-12-24 10:59:26','',0,'http://www.pingwest.us/?p=1',0,'post','',0),(6,2,'2012-12-11 01:54:32','2012-12-11 01:54:32','这是示范页面。页面和博客文章不同，它的位置是固定的，通常会在站点导航栏显示。很多用户都创建一个“关于”页面，向访客介绍自己。例如，个人博客通常有类似这样的介绍：\n\n<blockquote>欢迎！我白天是个邮递员，晚上就是个有抱负的演员。这是我的博客。我住在天朝的帝都，有条叫做 Jack 的狗。</blockquote>\n\n... 公司博客可以这样写：\n\n<blockquote>XYZ Doohickey 公司成立于 1971 年，自从建立以来，我们一直向社会贡献着优秀 doohicky。我们的公司总部位于天朝魔都，有着超过两千名员工，对魔都政府税收有着巨大贡献。</blockquote>\n\n您可以访问<a href=\"http://www.pingwest.us/wp-admin/\">仪表盘</a>，删除本页面，然后添加您自己的内容。祝您使用愉快！','示例页面','','publish','open','open','','sample-page-2','','','2012-12-11 01:54:32','2012-12-11 01:54:32','',0,'http://www.pingwest.us/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(7,2,'2012-12-11 16:50:46','2012-12-11 08:50:46','据台湾媒体报道，全球最大的多媒体应用软件公司Adobe已于上周五关闭台湾分公司，连台湾总经理黄中平也在裁员名单之列，不少在台外商公司员工听闻此事也感到人心惶惶。','Adobe已于上周五关闭台湾分公司','','publish','closed','open','','%e6%8d%ae%e5%8f%b0%e6%b9%be%e5%aa%92%e4%bd%93%e6%8a%a5%e9%81%93%ef%bc%8c%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e7%9a%84%e5%a4%9a%e5%aa%92%e4%bd%93%e5%ba%94%e7%94%a8%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8ad','','','2012-12-24 22:18:08','2012-12-24 14:18:08','',0,'http://www.pingwest.us/?p=5',0,'post','',0),(332,2,'2012-12-11 17:11:55','2012-12-11 09:11:55',